    <abstract>
      <t>   This document describes a syntax for the Connect-Info attribute used
   with the Remote Authentication Dial In User Service (RADIUS)
   protocol, enabling clients to provide servers information pertaining
   to the operation of an IEEE 802.11 wireless network.

